cs.ualberta.ca.tunein

Class Commenter

  • java.lang.Object
    • Application
      • cs.ualberta.ca.tunein.Commenter

  • public class Commenter
extends Application
    Model Commenter Class: This is a model class for the user that creates a comment. This class is not complete yet. The only attributes right now is a name for the commenter. To access this class throughout the whole app you can use String username = ((Commenter) this.getApplication()).getName(); to retrieve the username and String id = ((Commenter) this.getApplication()).getUniqueID(); to get the id.
